snippet.description:
Family Banned From United Airlines After This
Subscribe Here ☛ http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

A family has been banned for life by United Airlines when their 2 year old daughter refused to wear a mask. The family was apparently travelling from Colorado to New Jersey over the weekend and told the attendant that they had flown all summer with no issues prior to this.
